		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.brandyborges.com/?p=656</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[I think I remember being 17. I&#8217;m sure I felt invincible. Two turned 17 last month. I look at him and all I see is a smiling, little boy, curious to learn about everything. He&#8217;s growing up. I don&#8217;t know when it happened. He has everything, well, anything he needs. He works and also makes <a class="more-link" href="http://www.brandyborges.com/?p=656">Continue reading <i class="fa fa-chevron-right"></i></a>]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>I think I remember being 17. I&#8217;m sure I felt invincible.<br />
Two turned 17 last month. I look at him and all I see is a smiling, little boy, curious to learn about everything. He&#8217;s growing up. I don&#8217;t know when it happened.<br />
He has everything, well, anything he needs. He works and also makes money from some things he doesn&#8217;t online. There is nothing I can buy him&#8230; I have no money. He knows and understands, but I feel bad that I can&#8217;t even celebrate his birthday by giving him a gift.<br />
So this year I&#8217;ve been watching the Northern Lights. They have sensors and instruments that predict it. Well, I had been following it and there was a prediction that they were going to be able to be seen in Eau Claire. So I surprised him, told him about it, showed him the app and the data, and we headed up north (2 hours).<br />
To make a long story short, we waited and never saw them. I was so disappointed. I just wanted to do something special for him.<br />
Someday I&#8217;ll give him something magnificent&#8230; something that isn&#8217;t money, but worth the world to him. Someday&#8230;</p>
<p><a class="a2a_button_facebook" href="http://www.addtoany.com/add_to/facebook?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.brandyborges.com%2F%3Fp%3D656&amp;linkname=Seventeen" title="Facebook" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_button_twitter" href="http://www.addtoany.com/add_to/twitter?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.brandyborges.com%2F%3Fp%3D656&amp;linkname=Seventeen" title="Twitter" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_button_google_plus" href="http://www.addtoany.com/add_to/google_plus?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.brandyborges.com%2F%3Fp%3D656&amp;linkname=Seventeen" title="Google+" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_button_pinterest" href="http://www.addtoany.com/add_to/pinterest?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.brandyborges.com%2F%3Fp%3D656&amp;linkname=Seventeen" title="Pinterest" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_dd a2a_target addtoany_share_save" href="https://www.addtoany.com/share#url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.brandyborges.com%2F%3Fp%3D656&amp;title=Seventeen" id="wpa2a_8"></a></p>]]></content:encoded>
