		<item>
		<title>We&#8217;re Back to Four</title>
		<link>http://www.brandyborges.com/?p=652</link>
		<pubDate>Wed, 11 Nov 2015 03:36:20 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Brandyoldfashion]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Family Dynamic]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Family]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[One]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.brandyborges.com/?p=652</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[One moved out this last January. In the last 10 months, we&#8217;ve adjusted to being down to 3 people in the house, but all of that changed. One texted me this last Sunday while I was a church asking me to come get him and all his belongings. Two and I made the 3 hour trip <a class="more-link" href="http://www.brandyborges.com/?p=652">Continue reading <i class="fa fa-chevron-right"></i></a>]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>One moved out this last January. In the last 10 months, we&#8217;ve adjusted to being down to 3 people in the house, but all of that changed. One texted me this last Sunday while I was a church asking me to come get him and all his belongings. Two and I made the 3 hour trip there by 1:30 in the morning, packed until 4, and started to head here. We, by chance, ran into my dad at the gas station / restaurant where we stopped to get gas and my dad offered to buy us breakfast. We finished eating, got on the road and finally arrived here by 9 am. We left everything and went right to bed. By time I fell asleep, I had been awake for 28 hours.<br />
Today we cleaned and rearranged the garage to fit his car parts and tools. We&#8217;re now discussing how to add a room along side my trailer so that he&#8217;d have a room to stay in.<br />
It is not how I planned, but it&#8217;s nice to have all 3 under my roof again. They&#8217;ll always be my babies, no matter how old or big they get. It feels like we&#8217;re whole again&#8230; complete.</p>
<p><a class="a2a_button_facebook" href="http://www.addtoany.com/add_to/facebook?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.brandyborges.com%2F%3Fp%3D652&amp;linkname=We%E2%80%99re%20Back%20to%20Four" title="Facebook" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_button_twitter" href="http://www.addtoany.com/add_to/twitter?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.brandyborges.com%2F%3Fp%3D652&amp;linkname=We%E2%80%99re%20Back%20to%20Four" title="Twitter" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_button_google_plus" href="http://www.addtoany.com/add_to/google_plus?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.brandyborges.com%2F%3Fp%3D652&amp;linkname=We%E2%80%99re%20Back%20to%20Four" title="Google+" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_button_pinterest" href="http://www.addtoany.com/add_to/pinterest?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.brandyborges.com%2F%3Fp%3D652&amp;linkname=We%E2%80%99re%20Back%20to%20Four" title="Pinterest" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_dd a2a_target addtoany_share_save" href="https://www.addtoany.com/share#url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.brandyborges.com%2F%3Fp%3D652&amp;title=We%E2%80%99re%20Back%20to%20Four" id="wpa2a_12"></a></p>]]></content:encoded>
