		<title>Dipping Down</title>
		<link>http://www.brandyborges.com/?p=650</link>
		<pubDate>Thu, 05 Nov 2015 02:37:27 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Brandyoldfashion]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Rant]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Family]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Food]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.brandyborges.com/?p=650</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[There is so much that I want to do. My wall is all mudded and sanded in the living room and ready for the wanes-coating and paint, but I haven&#8217;t been able to do much in the last few days. My headaches are back and when I woke up this morning I forgot to make <a class="more-link" href="http://www.brandyborges.com/?p=650">Continue reading <i class="fa fa-chevron-right"></i></a>]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>There is so much that I want to do.<br />
My wall is all mudded and sanded in the living room and ready for the wanes-coating and paint, but I haven&#8217;t been able to do much in the last few days.<br />
My headaches are back and when I woke up this morning I forgot to make sure my hips were in their sockets and as I was walking to the bathroom, the left hip popped back into place and I haven&#8217;t been able to bear weight on it all day.<br />
I have food from the pantry I went to on Monday, but I can&#8217;t stand long enough to make anything.<br />
With my check on the first of the month, I paid all my bills, but I have no money left.<br />
It just seems like I can&#8217;t get ahead&#8230; I can&#8217;t accomplish anything&#8230; I can&#8217;t get one step forward.</p>
<p>And I&#8217;m so lonely. I know that God will send the right one for me at the perfect time, but patience is not my strong suit.<br />
Maybe tomorrow will be better&#8230;.. just maybe.</p>
<p><a class="a2a_button_facebook" href="http://www.addtoany.com/add_to/facebook?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.brandyborges.com%2F%3Fp%3D650&amp;linkname=Dipping%20Down" title="Facebook" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_button_twitter" href="http://www.addtoany.com/add_to/twitter?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.brandyborges.com%2F%3Fp%3D650&amp;linkname=Dipping%20Down" title="Twitter" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_button_google_plus" href="http://www.addtoany.com/add_to/google_plus?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.brandyborges.com%2F%3Fp%3D650&amp;linkname=Dipping%20Down" title="Google+" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_button_pinterest" href="http://www.addtoany.com/add_to/pinterest?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.brandyborges.com%2F%3Fp%3D650&amp;linkname=Dipping%20Down" title="Pinterest" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_dd a2a_target addtoany_share_save" href="https://www.addtoany.com/share#url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.brandyborges.com%2F%3Fp%3D650&amp;title=Dipping%20Down" id="wpa2a_14"></a></p>]]></content:encoded>
